# Example Environment Variables
PORT=3000
MONGO_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017/library
EMAIL_USER=your-email@gmail.com
EMAIL_PASS=your-email-password

# Instructions For EMAIL_PASS:
# 1. Replace 'your-email@gmail.com' with your Gmail address.
# 2. Replace 'your-app-password' with the App Password generated from your Google Account.
#    - Go to your Google Account settings.
#    - Navigate to 'Security' and enable '2-Step Verification' if not already enabled.
#    - Under 'App Passwords,' generate a new password for your application.
#    - Use this App Password here.
# 3. Save the file as .env in the root directory of your project.